Package com.shinobicontrols.chart.axis

Class Summary
Axis An Axis controls the Range that is displayed by the Chart and draws the Tick and GridLine objects that are associated with this Axis.
Axis.Settings<TSettings extends Axis.Settings<TSettings>> The Axis.Settings for an Axis
AxisInteractions Handles all the Touch Events for an Axis.
CategoryAxis An implementation of Axis that controls a CategoryRange of CategoryDataSeriesItems.
CategoryAxis.Settings The CategoryAxis.Settings for a CategoryAxis
CategoryTick An extension of MajorTick for Ticks on a CategoryAxis
GridLine A GridLine to be displayed on the PlotArea of the Chart.
GridLine.Settings The GridLine.Settings for a GridLine
MajorGridLine An implementation of GridLine that corresponds to the position of the MajorTicks on an Axis.
MajorGridLine.Settings The MajorGridLine.Settings for a MajorGridLine
MajorTick An implementation of Tick for the MajorTick marks along an Axis.
MajorTick.Settings The MajorTick.Settings for a MajorTick
MinorTick Experimental feature:
An implementation of Tick for the MinorTick marks along an Axis.
MinorTick.Settings The MinorTick.Settings for a MinorTick
NumberAxis<TDataSeriesItem extends DataSeriesItem,TRange extends BaseRange> A base class for an Axis that controls a (numerical) BaseRange.
NumberAxis.Settings The NumberAxis.Settings for a NumberAxis
Tick A Tick encompasses the tick mark line drawn on an Axis as well as the label for the value it represents.
Tick.Settings The Tick.Settings for a Tick
ValueAxis An implementation of NumberAxis that controls a DefaultRange of ValueDataSeriesItems.
XAxis An implementation of NumberAxis that controls a DefaultRange of XDataSeriesItems.
YAxis An implementation of NumberAxis that controls a DefaultRange of YDataSeriesItems.
 

Enum Summary
Tick.LabelOrientation Enumeration of the possible orientations a label for a Tick can take.
